- No changes at all.


1.0beta2 - Tuesday 09 May 2006
^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^

- Added the removeRecursive method to recursively delete directories.
- Fixed a bug in findRecursive where hidden files were not found.


1.0beta1 - Wednesday 19 April 2006
